            "content": "<p>While proper oral hygiene is essential to preventing gingivitis, there are many other factors that can influence whether or not youâ€™ll get gingivitis. These include age, nutrition, tobacco use, infections, diabetes, and more. Use SmartMouthâ„˘ Clinical mouthwash twice a day. Other than improving your oral hygiene and diet, this is one of the best ways to eliminate germs and sulfur production in your mouth.</p>"
